doc.previous: Dartmouth alumni in academia include Stuart Kauffman and Jeffrey Weeks both recipients of MacArthur Fellowships commonly called genius grants 220 221 Dartmouth has also graduated three Nobel Prize winners Owen Chamberlain Physics 1959 222 K Barry Sharpless Chemistry 2001 223 and George Davis Snell Physiology or Medicine 1980 224 Educators include the current chancellor of the University of California San Diego Marye Anne Fox PhD in Chemistry 1974 225 founding president of Vassar College Milo Parker Jewett 226 founder and first president of Bates College Oren B Cheney 227 founder and first president of Kenyon College Philander Chase 228 first professor of Wabash College Caleb Mills 229 and former president of Union College Charles Augustus Aiken 230 231 Nine of Dartmouth s 17 presidents were alumni of the College 232
